languages.text: {n}Лицо Хейнрикса чудовищно искажается — кожа до предела натягивается на костях черепа, его голос звенит от ярости.{/n} "Кей-морагх... не пытайся пробраться сквозь раскинутую паутину, мон-кай! Исполни то, зачем ты здесь и находишься!"

traits.locale_text: "Ты как назойливая муха, уверенная в том, что проберется меж паучьих лап, не угодив в паутину! Соберись, мон-кай, и исполни то, зачем я тебя сюда притащил!"
traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: {n}Heinrix's face contorts monstrously, his skin stretched to the limit across the bones of his skull, his voice ringing with fury.{/n} "Kae-morag... do not try to squeeze between the strands of the web, mon-keigh! Do what you were brought here for!"

Faites ce pour quoi vous avez été {mf|amené|amenée} ici ! »

languages.text: {n}海因里希的脸怪异地扭曲着，头上的皮肤似乎已经伸展到了极限，声音也愤怒地颤抖着。{/n}“该死……你真是敬酒不吃吃罚酒，猴子！别忘了你原本的职责！”

languages.text: {n}ハインリックスの顔が怪物のように歪み、皮膚が頭蓋骨に張り付くように限界まで引き伸ばされ、怒りに満ちた声が響いた。 {/n}「カエ＝モラグ…網の繊維の間に無理やり押し入るようなマネはするなよ、モン＝ケイ！ここに連れてこられた目的を果たせ！」

languages.text: {n}Heinrix' Miene verdüstert sich auf monströse Weise. Seine Haut spannt sich fast bis zum Zerreißen um die Knochen seines Schädels und seine Stimme dröhnt vor Wut.{/n} "Kae-morag ... versucht Euch nicht zwischen den Fäden des Netzes durchzuquetschen, Chem-Pan-Sey! Macht das, wofür Ihr hergebracht wurdet!"
languages.original_text: {n}Heinrix's face contorts monstrously, his skin stretched to the limit across the bones of his skull, his voice ringing with fury.{/n} "Kae-morag... do not try to squeeze between the strands of the web, mon-keigh! Do what you were brought here for!"

traits.locale_text: {n}Heinrix' Miene verdüstert sich auf monströse Weise, seine Haut spannt sich extrem um die Knochen seines Schädels und seine Stimme zeigt seine Wut.{/n} "Kae-moragh ... versucht Euch nicht zwischen die Kiefer einer Spinne und die Fäden ihres Netzes zu quetschen, Chem-Pan-Sey! Macht das, wofür Ihr hergebracht wurdet!"
traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: {n}El rostro de Heinrix se contrae monstruosamente, su piel se estira hasta el límite de los huesos de su cráneo y su voz resuena cargada de furia.{/n} «Kae-morag... ¡no intentes escurrirte entre las hebras de la telaraña, mon-keigh! ¡Haz aquello para lo que te hemos traído!».
languages.original_text: {n}Heinrix's face contorts monstrously, his skin stretched to the limit across the bones of his skull, his voice ringing with fury.{/n} "Kae-morag... do not try to squeeze between the strands of the web, mon-keigh! Do what you were brought here for!"

traits.locale_text: {n}El rostro de Heinrix se contrae monstruosamente, su piel se estira hasta el límite de los huesos de su cráneo y su voz resuena cargada de furia.{/n} «Kae-moragh... ¡no intentes escurrirte entre las mandíbulas de la araña y las hebras de su tela, mon-keigh! ¡Haz aquello para lo que te hemos traído!».
traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: {n}Heinrix'in yüzü buruşup canavarımsı bir hâl alıyor; derisi, kafasındaki kemikleri zorla içeride tutuyormuşçasına geriliyor. Nihayet sesi öfkeyle yankılanıyor.{/n} "Kae-morag. Ağa takıldın bir kere, kaçışın yok. Buraya getirilme sebebin neyse ona odaklan!"
languages.original_text: {n}Heinrix's face contorts monstrously, his skin stretched to the limit across the bones of his skull, his voice ringing with fury.{/n} "Kae-morag... do not try to squeeze between the strands of the web, mon-keigh! Do what you were brought here for!"

traits.locale_text: {n}Heinrix'in yüzü buruşup canavarımsı bir hâl alıyor, derisi kafasındaki kemikler boyunca sınırları zorlarcasına geriliyor, sesi öfkeyle yankılanıyor.{/n} "Kae-morag. Ağdaki bölümlerin arasına girmeye çalışma mon-keigh! Buraya getirilme sebebin neyse ona odaklan!"
traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion
